215
00:11:44,541 --> 00:11:45,416
Sì.

216
00:11:46,208 --> 00:11:48,333
Fantastico. Complimenti.

217
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:50,708
Ci vediamo dentro.

218
00:11:55,416 --> 00:11:57,458
Dai, si va in Canada.

219
00:11:59,291 --> 00:12:01,750
{\an8}<i>Lavoro per Ray Loewen.
Freme per conoscerla.</i>

220
00:12:01,750 --> 00:12:05,708
